    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it is in total mint condition! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. It drives like an absolute dream and is ready for a new home. You seriously won't find one cleaner than this! I'm happy to answer any questions or show you around the car, so just send me a message and let's chat!",
      "price": 43500.0,
