    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 996.2 Carrera 4S is a superlative example of the wide-body, naturally aspirated 911. Powered by the M96.03 3.6L flat-six with VarioCam Plus, this engine delivers seamless power through a G96 6-speed manual transaxle. The mechanical integrity is absolute; the IMS bearing has been proactively replaced with a ceramic dual-row upgrade, and the rear main seal is dry. The chassis features the factory M030 sport suspension, providing surgical turn-in via the hydraulic rack-and-pinion steering. Finished in original paint with no evidence of track-use heat cycling, the braking system utilizes 4-piston monoblock calipers over cross-drilled rotors with zero lipping. This is a turn-key, investment-grade machine for the technical purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
